@startuml
title 社区互动时序图

actor 用户 as User
participant ":社区页面" as Frontend
participant ":FeedbackController" as FC
participant ":FeedbackService" as FS
participant ":FeedbackDao" as FD
participant ":DB" as DB

User -> Frontend: 1:发表/点赞评论
Frontend -> FC: 2:评论/点赞请求
FC -> FS: 3:提交评论或切换点赞
FS -> FD: 4:增删评论表或点赞表
FD -> DB: 5:读写对应数据表
DB --> Frontend: 6:返回结果
Frontend --> User: 7:更新页面

User -> Frontend: 8:喜欢/收藏歌曲
Frontend -> FC: 9:喜欢/收藏请求
FC -> FS: 10:切换喜欢或收藏状态
FS -> FD: 11:增删反馈记录
FD -> DB: 12:读写反馈表
DB --> Frontend: 13:返回状态
Frontend --> User: 14:更新图标

User -> Frontend: 15:查看社区动态/收藏
Frontend -> FC: 16:查询请求
FC -> FS: 17:获取数据
FS -> FD: 18:联表查询评论/用户/音乐
FD -> DB: 19:联表查询
DB --> Frontend: 20:返回列表

@enduml
